<h2>Corrupting items</h2>
<div class="ui segment">
    <h3>Introduction</h3>
    <p>Corrupting items can be very profitable when done right.</p>
    <p>Depending on the item level of the item you have a certain % chance to hit the corruption you want.</p>
    <p>All items have their own optimal corruption ilvl</p>
</div>
