<div class="ui segment">
    <h3>Lastly</h3>
 
        <p>All the different items on the list have their own different optimal item levels</p>
        <p>refer to <a target="_blank" href="https://pathofexile.gamepedia.com/Vaal_Orb">Wikipedia VaalOrb</a> for them</p>

 
            <p>You want to gather from 20-100 items to corrupt before you start the process.</p>
        <p>Early league it is easy to get low level items and this is when you should start sniping them off the poe.trade.</p>
        <p>One thing to note is that if you happen to have a perfectly rolled item it will go for 50-100% more price.</p>
        <p>Sniping perfect items early league is recommended since even if you don’t end up corrupting them you will get your money back 20x</p>

 
            <p>When corrupting bows i don’t tend to 6 socket or color them before hand because this can be done afterwards with lvl 8 vorici.</p>
        <p>It will cost more but in the long run it will be cheaper.</p>


    
